create-kdna-web-app is a project scaffolding CLI for KDNA-integrated
web applications. Generated projects include @aikdna/kdna-web-server,
@aikdna/kdna-web-client, and @aikdna/kdna-react pre-configured with
a working validate → plan-load → load → consume flow.

